{"word":"κοινωνέω","slug":"κοινωνέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰοινωνέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κοινωνός\">κοινωνός</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘have a part in’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> share <a href='B:520 15:27'>Ro 15:27</a>; <a href='B:570 4:15'>Phil 4:15</a>; <a href='B:650 2:14'>Hb 2:14</a>; <a href='B:670 4:13'>1 Pt 4:13</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> make common cause with <a href='B:520 12:13'>Ro 12:13</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp> participate (in) <a href='B:610 5:22'>1 Ti 5:22</a>; <a href='B:700 1:1'>2 J 11</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘give a share in’,<b>share <a href='B:550 6:6'>Gal 6:6</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘cause to be common’, <b>make ritually defiled/unclean <a href='B:470 15:11'>Mt 15:11</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κοινόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κοινωνία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}